properties.property: The allied force is prepared to stage an invasion of the Krovnork base. Their surface armies will be crippled and unable to threaten us if we suceed. Mission objectives: -Secure the area. -Eliminate threats.
Our warriors are deployed. The Krovnorks cannot be reasoned with, we must destroy them for the safety of the mission.
The Krovnork invasion has been cut off. Orbital forces will prevent further landings.
Hold back the Krovnork reinforcements for one minute.
The shameful infection cannot be allowed to taint this planet any longer... Our warriors rage from the betrayal of its creator.
